    <head>Biographical Note</head>
<p>Benjamin Harvey Brush (1820-1853), son of Joshua and Sarah (Ralph) Brush, was born in Smithtown, Long Island, N.Y.</p>  </bioghist>
  <scopecontent id="aspace_26f0615ba863b72f40a8f5648875876e">
